{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":891,"text":"Have you ever been asked\nby your Chinese friend,"},{"time":3713,"text":"\"What is your zodiac sign?\""},{"time":5947,"text":"Don't think they are making small talk."},{"time":8456,"text":"If you say, \"I'm a Monkey,\""},{"time":10407,"text":"they immediately know"},{"time":11790,"text":"you are either 24, 36, 48 or 60 years old."}]},{"cues":[{"time":15210,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":16240,"text":"Asking a zodiac sign is a polite way\nof asking your age."}]},{"cues":[{"time":20616,"text":"By revealing your zodiac sign,\nyou are also being evaluated."},{"time":24529,"text":"Judgments are being made\nabout your fortune or misfortune,"},{"time":28593,"text":"your personality, career prospects"},{"time":30995,"text":"and how you will do in a given year."},{"time":33322,"text":"If you share you and your\npartner's animal signs,"},{"time":36242,"text":"they will paint a picture in their mind\nabout your private life."},{"time":40725,"text":"Maybe you don't believe\nin the Chinese zodiac."},{"time":43372,"text":"As a quarter of the world population\nis influenced by it,"},{"time":47227,"text":"you'd be wise to do something about that."}]},{"cues":[{"time":50406,"text":"So what is the Chinese zodiac, exactly?"},{"time":53991,"text":"Most Westerners think\nof Greco-Roman zodiac,"},{"time":57211,"text":"the signs divided into 12 months."},{"time":59973,"text":"The Chinese zodiac is different."},{"time":61948,"text":"It's a 12-year cycle labeled with animals,"},{"time":65150,"text":"starting with a Rat and ending with a Pig,"},{"time":67750,"text":"and has no association\nwith constellations."},{"time":71663,"text":"For example, if you were born\nin 1975, you are a Rabbit."},{"time":77273,"text":"Can you see your zodiac sign there?"},{"time":80139,"text":"Our Chinese ancestors constructed\na very complicated theoretical framework"},{"time":85448,"text":"based on yin and yang, the five elements\nand the 12 zodiac animals."},{"time":90486,"text":"Over thousands of years,"},{"time":92305,"text":"this popular culture has affected\npeople's major decisions,"},{"time":96801,"text":"such as naming, marriage, giving birth\nand attitude towards each other."},{"time":102409,"text":"And some of the implications\nare quite amazing."}]},{"cues":[{"time":106248,"text":"The Chinese believe certain animals\nget on better than the others."},{"time":111147,"text":"So parents choose specific years\nto give birth to babies,"},{"time":115865,"text":"because they believe the team effort\nby the right combination of animals"},{"time":120811,"text":"can give prosperity to families."},{"time":123667,"text":"We even refer to the zodiac\nwhen entering into romantic relations."},{"time":128630,"text":"I'm a Pig; I should have perfect romance\nwith Tigers, Goats and Rabbits."},{"time":135425,"text":"Chinese people believe some animals\nare natural enemies."},{"time":139536,"text":"As a Pig, I need\nto be careful with a Snake."},{"time":143102,"text":"Raise your hand if you are a Snake."},{"time":145726,"text":"Let's have a chat later."}]},{"cues":[{"time":147283,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":148702,"text":"We believe some animals\nare luckier than the others,"},{"time":151969,"text":"such as the Dragon."},{"time":153688,"text":"Unlike the Western tradition,"},{"time":155570,"text":"the Chinese Dragon is a symbol\nfor power, strength and wealth."},{"time":160178,"text":"It's everyone's dream\nto have a Dragon baby."},{"time":163359,"text":"Jack Ma's parents\nmust have been very proud."},{"time":166499,"text":"And they are not the only ones."},{"time":168085,"text":"In 2012, the Year of the Dragon,"},{"time":171006,"text":"the birthrate in China,\nHong Kong and Taiwan"},{"time":173329,"text":"increased by five percent."},{"time":175596,"text":"That means another\none million more babies."},{"time":180497,"text":"With a traditional\npreference to baby boys,"},{"time":183434,"text":"the boy-girl ratio that year\nwas 120 to 100."},{"time":188431,"text":"When those Dragon boys grow up,"},{"time":190219,"text":"they will face much more severe\ncompetition in love and job markets."}]},{"cues":[{"time":195669,"text":"According to the BBC and the Chinese\ngovernment's press release,"},{"time":199607,"text":"January 2015 saw a peak\nof Cesarean sections."},{"time":204835,"text":"Why?"},{"time":206726,"text":"That was the last month\nfor the Year of the Horse."},{"time":210161,"text":"It's not because they like horses so much,"},{"time":212787,"text":"it's because they try to avoid\nhaving unlucky Goat babies."}]},{"cues":[{"time":216280,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":217382,"text":"If you are a Goat, please don't feel bad."},{"time":220185,"text":"Those are Goat babies."},{"time":221939,"text":"They don't look like losers to me."}]},{"cues":[{"time":224073,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":225262,"text":"Tiger is another undesirable animal,"},{"time":228048,"text":"due to its volatile temperament."},{"time":230337,"text":"Many Chinese regions\nsaw a sharp decline of birthrate"},{"time":234214,"text":"during those years."},{"time":236122,"text":"Perhaps one should consider\nzodiac in reverse,"},{"time":239816,"text":"as those Tiger and Goat babies\nwill face much less competition."},{"time":244044,"text":"Maybe they are the lucky ones."},{"time":248055,"text":"I went through the Forbes\ntop 300 richest people in the world,"},{"time":252539,"text":"and it's interesting to see"},{"time":254596,"text":"the most undesirable two animals,\nthe Goat and Tiger,"},{"time":258198,"text":"are at the top of the chart,"},{"time":260544,"text":"even higher than the Dragon."},{"time":262351,"text":"So maybe we should consider,"},{"time":264495,"text":"maybe it's much better\nto have less competition."}]},{"cues":[{"time":268384,"text":"One last but interesting point:"},{"time":270429,"text":"many Chinese people make\ntheir investment decisions"},{"time":273286,"text":"based on the zodiac sign index."},{"time":276611,"text":"Although the belief and tradition\nof the zodiac sign"},{"time":280300,"text":"has been over thousands of years,"},{"time":283051,"text":"the trend of using it\nin making major decisions"},{"time":286369,"text":"did not really happen\nuntil the past few decades."},{"time":289934,"text":"Our ancestors were very busy\nsurviving poverty, drought,"},{"time":294354,"text":"famine, riot, disease and civil war."},{"time":298028,"text":"And finally, Chinese people\nhave the time, wealth and technology"},{"time":303814,"text":"to create an ideal life\nthey've always wanted."},{"time":307604,"text":"The collective decision\nmade by 1.3 billion people"},{"time":311275,"text":"has caused the fluctuation in economics\nand demand on everything,"},{"time":315850,"text":"from health care and education\nto property and consumer goods."},{"time":321092,"text":"As China plays such an important role\nin the global economy and geopolitics,"},{"time":326090,"text":"the decisions made based on the zodiac\nand other Chinese traditions"},{"time":330223,"text":"end up impacting everyone\naround the world."}]},{"cues":[{"time":335203,"text":"Are there any Monkeys here?"},{"time":338030,"text":"2016 is the Year of the Monkey."},{"time":341220,"text":"Monkeys are clever, curious,\ncreative and mischievous."}]},{"cues":[{"time":346953,"text":"Thank you."}]},{"cues":[{"time":348135,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}